Add two unpack helpers next to f16_bits_to_f32 (after ~:84). Little-endian (all NVIDIA GPUs): a 32-bit word holds the even-d f16 in its low 16 bits, odd-d in its high 16 bits.
```c
__device__ __forceinline__ float f16lo(unsigned int w){ return f16_bits_to_f32((unsigned short)(w & 0xffffu)); }
__device__ __forceinline__ float f16hi(unsigned int w){ return f16_bits_to_f32((unsigned short)(w >> 16)); }
```

